updates.update_content:
I got an update from Dave our production chief and I wanted to share the good news with you. 
All Dead Reckoning Color proofs have been approved and authorized our factories to begin mass production as of today. This means not only cards, but all tokens, punchboard, the cube-tower ship, packaging, and everything else! WoHoo!!!
During the "mass production" step a few other things will happen;
